  "description": "Aurum's revelation. Shimmer feedback at 0.82 with size 0.9 and octave balance at 0.7 creates an ever-ascending reverb tail — the Shepard tone of reverb. Each note feeds back through the octave-up pitch shifter, building an infinite staircase of light. The Guru says: this is the sound of looking up and never finding the ceiling. Transcendent.",
